entries.femaleVariant: Clogged toilets, shit beer... Remind me why I let you drag me to this place?
'Cause you're a decent choom, one. And two, still the best spot in this hood.
We could still try somewhere else for a change...
Sure, fine with me. Where to?
Well, maybe... Maybe somewhere in Charter Hill?
Ha ha! Sure, soon as my long lost ganic aunt leaves me all her scratch.
'Ey, come on. How much can one beer cost in the Hill?
